attributes.Long form description: The student rotates the table and starts unscrewing the top hex socket heads of the each leg with an Allen wrench, he starts with the first leg, then the second one; now the student rotates the table, and unscrews the rest of the hex socket heads of the table, until he's able to remove the top of the table. Next, the student starts unscrewing the middle hex socket heads of the first leg, and removes it. He continues to unscrew the middle hex socket heads of the second leg and then removes it. The student rotates the table once more, and unscrews the middle hex socket heads of the third leg and removes. Finally, the student rotates for the last time the table and unscrews the middle hex socket heads of the fourth  leg and removes it.
